dct_description_sm: State New Jersey map color coded according to all the electric companies that were operating in the state as of December 1, 1928. Pair of indexes show lists of companies and municipal plants alongside the counties each operated in. Henry B. Kummel is noted as the State Geologist under the Division of Geology and Waters.
